headline: MetLife Pet Insurance Collaborates with Petstablished to Make Pet Coverage Easy at Adoption
summary: NEW YORK, December 17, 2025--MetLife Pet Insurance (MetLife) today announced a new exclusive collaboration with Petstablished, the industry-leading provider of management software for animal welfare organizations (AWOs), to offer pet insurance quotes directly within the adoption and registration process on the Petstablished platform, which supports over 1,000 AWOs and facilitates more than 160,000 adoptions annually.
